{"tid":2445729,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–雞蛋出現雙黃是天然或是人為？","createTime":"2021-03-14T00:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T17:06:34.000Z","uid":38861,"like":49,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"a0ec93ebce10da29a1d086578327289c3de95979","tid":2445729,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T00:36:37.000Z","msg":"一隻雞蛋裡頭有雙蛋黃，究竟是人為所致還是天然隨機發生的呢?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/24gfXzM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F24gfXzM.jpg&h=41bb324f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）在回答之前，我們需要了解一下雞蛋在母雞裡生產的過程。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wDJxZN9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwDJxZN9.png&h=66e4341b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當卵子從卵巢(Ovary)排出後，便會在Infundibulum逗留約15-30分鐘。<br />\n若果在此時遇上精子的話，便會進行受精，生出來的雞蛋有機會可孵出小雞。<br />\n不過無論受精與否，卵子隨後便抵達Magnum，在該位置的細胞會釋出各種蛋白質，圍繞著卵子的蛋黃製作蛋白，這過程歷時約2-3小時。<br />\n<br />\n之後就會到達Isthmus，花費將1-2小時形成蛋殼內膜。<br />\n<br />\n最後就會來到Shell gland，逗留接近18-22小時，形成含豐富鈣質（鈣質佔蛋殼95%成份）的蛋殼，這同時亦是坊間為何經常利用蛋殼作施肥的原因。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）有科學家對雞隻進行實驗。在實驗1裡頭，往雞隻增加注射雌激素的話，雞蛋出現雙黃的機率亦會隨之增加。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YkzEEOc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYkzEEOc.png&h=06fa96b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但是，這現象並沒有出現在實驗2裡頭。<br />\n<br />\n文中作者表示實驗1所用的雞隻較實驗2的為年輕足足一個月有多，而同時的確亦有不同證據(Ref3)指出年輕雞隻所生的雞蛋出現雙黃的機率亦較高;<br />\n年輕(4-12.5%)vs年長(1.12-3.53%)。<br />\n<br />\n這相信是年輕母雞的排卵及生產雞蛋的機制尚未完善，例如不經意地造就雙黃聚在一起共同在Magnum製作蛋白等，因而造就雙黃情況。<br />\n<br />\n之於荷爾蒙方面，雌激素能刺激雞隻肝臟製作更多釀成蛋黃及脂肪的原料，在年輕雞隻中亦能增加生產錯誤的機率，釀成雙黃局面。<br />\n<br />\n但相信基於是年老的母雞已發展出完善的排卵程序、又或是對雌激素已失去敏感度，出現雙黃的機率並不沒有受雌激素影響得到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfB4w7aMtX%2B%2FJ%2BUdoe8qorTI%3D&h=563b8be1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfB4w7aMtX%2B%2FJ%2BUdoe8qorTI%3D&h=123fca98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"http://www2.ca.uky.edu/agcomm/pubs/ASC/ASC201/ASC201.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.ca.uky.edu%2Fagcomm%2Fpubs%2FASC%2FASC201%2FASC201.pdf&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfB4w7aMtX%2B%2FJ%2BUdoe8qorTI%3D&h=a051c54e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.ca.uky.edu/agcomm/pubs/ASC/ASC201/ASC201.pdf</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0032579119512536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0032579119512536&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfB4w7aMtX%2B%2FJ%2BUdoe8qorTI%3D&h=71ce8000\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0032579119512536</a><br />\nRef3:<a href=\"https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/00439339.2020.1729671\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1080%2F00439339.2020.1729671&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfB4w7aMtX%2B%2FJ%2BUdoe8qorTI%3D&h=41dc51b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/00439339.2020.1729671</a>"},{"pid":"94ae952be7a424da779bfab24023ca4b3d454631","tid":2445729,"uid":97887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T00:44:06.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d63296b0d87598ae3ed205b4198e5f2a0f7fe339","tid":2445729,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T00:46:16.000Z","msg":"咁母雞無受精都生蛋係自然定人為？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n物種無理由咁on9不斷無意義咁浪費資源能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849b7512ec26eb38e275a43a45b0ae6b66f5ac92","tid":2445729,"uid":379913,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T00:49:58.000Z","msg":"之前喺超級市場買過一盒泰國蛋<br />\n開第一隻雙黃以為好彩<br />\n點知開多兩隻都係雙黃<br />\n跟住開曬10隻都係雙黃<br />\n結果倒曬"},{"pid":"8d247b20123f14134ca912f1970020feaec7be69","tid":2445729,"uid":38861,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d63296b0d87598ae3ed205b4198e5f2a0f7fe339","tid":2445729,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T00:46:16.000Z","msg":"咁母雞無受精都生蛋係自然定人為？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n物種無理由咁on9不斷無意義咁浪費資源能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T01:17:55.000Z","msg":"或者要判斷受精定未受精的話，可能仲哂資源。"},{"pid":"004586edb01284ba1996284a70f01d763947ca50","tid":2445729,"uid":152598,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T01:26:20.000Z","msg":"即係點<br />\n你個總結係自然定人為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b2d6faaa38dbe0c8f0bf3e76be0e68a77e42d8","tid":2445729,"uid":152598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"849b7512ec26eb38e275a43a45b0ae6b66f5ac92","tid":2445729,"uid":379913,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T00:49:58.000Z","msg":